<h3>@ViewData["Title"]</h3>

<p>We collect personal information from you, which may include your:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Name</li>
    <li>Contact information</li>
    <li>Personal photos</li>
</ul>

<h4>Why we collect this information</h4>
<p>
    We collect your personal information to properly manage and conduct the school’s voting system,
    and to ensure that only eligible students are able to participate.
</p>

<h4>Who we share your information with</h4>
<p>
    Your information may be shared with the school to confirm your identity and verify that you are a member of the institution.
    Apart from this, your information will only be accessible to authorized staff involved in running the voting system.
</p>

<h4>Optional information</h4>
<ul>
    <li>If you choose not to upload a photo, a default profile image will be used.</li>
    <li>If you choose not to provide a personal description, your profile will remain blank. Please note, this may reduce your visibility and impact during the voting process.</li>
</ul>

<h4>How we protect your information</h4>
<p>
    We keep your information secure by encrypting passwords and restricting access only to certified staff.
</p>

<h4>Your rights</h4>
<p>
    You have the right to request a copy of any personal information we hold about you, and to ask for corrections if you believe it is inaccurate.
    To make a request, please contact us at:
